## ⚙️ How to Upload (GitHub Pages)
1. Go to your GitHub repository.
2. Click **Add File → Upload Files**.
3. Upload all files from this folder (including `/assets/`).
4. Commit changes.
5. Go to **Settings → Pages → Source → main → /(root)** → Save.
6. Your website will appear at:

---

## 🧠 How to Edit
- **Change Hero Image** → replace `assets/hero.jpg` with your new image.
- **Change Logo** → replace `assets/favicon.svg`.
- **Change WhatsApp** → search for `wa.me/` in index.html and update number.
- **Change Email** → edit email in the Contact section.
- **Change Domain** → update the footer link.

---

## 📧 EmailJS Integration
1. Go to [https://www.emailjs.com](https://www.emailjs.com)
2. Create your account → Add Gmail service → Create a new template.
3. Copy your:
- SERVICE_ID  
- TEMPLATE_ID  
- PUBLIC_KEY  
4. Replace placeholders in script (if added) inside `index.html`.

